Despite an anomalous peak exceeding the provisioned speed, there are no sustained congestion risks or bottlenecks. The link maintains 100% SLA compliance in the "Excellent" category, indicating consistent performance well below capacity for nearly all operational time.

**Conclusion**
The link should be significantly downgraded to a new provisioning target of 12 Mbps.
